channel.description:
[center][img]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/536/bensprojectrsps.webs.com/Logo25.png[/img][/center] Ben's project is a rsps that strives to provide the best staff and gameplay with all the new runescape content around. we are a rsps running 718/736 with all the new updated god wars dungeons and item and npc updated graphics. We have also reset the economy so the map is fresh and we have multiple custom maps for play also we have a fully working dominion tower!
[b]Progress:[/b] Released to public
[center][u][b]★ Features ★[/b][/u][/center] [center][b]-[/b] [b]100%[/b] weapon specs [b]-[/b] Custom royalty program with loyalty shop [b]-[/b] [b]100%[/b]working flasks, money pouch, summoning [b]-[/b] Fully updated 736 graphics [b]-[/b] Flawless Monster animations and sound [b]-[/b] Mature staff [b]-[/b] [b]Mini games:[/b] Dominion tower, Barrows, Fight caves, Fight kiln, Fight pit, Clan wars, and more [b]-[/b] Great Economy [b]-[/b] Hours of content [b]-[/b] Flawless item switching [b]-[/b] Bandos warshield, Bandos helmet, Armadyl crossbow, Armadyl buckler [b]-[/b] Working Squeal of Fortune [b]-[/b] Shops [b]-[/b] [b]PVM:[/b] Tormented Demons, KBD (Being Updated), QBD, Corp, GWD, Nex, and more [b]-[/b] Complete God Wars Remastered dungeons as well as nex [/center]
To download the client head over to [url=http://bensprojectrsps.webs.com]bensprojectrsps,webs.com[/url] and download the client to come join the community [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bD4-fXodAEA[/youtube] [/center] Pictures: [img]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/420/bensprojectrsps.webs.com/zammy.PNG[/img] - [img]http://d2bm3ljpacyxu8.cloudfront.net/width/420/bensprojectrsps.webs.com/nex.PNG[/img]
